		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">This article is about the short story and novel.  For the West End musical starring Michael Crawford, see <a href="/wiki/Charlie_and_Algernon" title="Charlie and Algernon">Charlie and Algernon</a>.  For the Kyosuke Himuro album, see <a href="/wiki/Flowers_for_Algernon_(album)" title="Flowers for Algernon (album)">Flowers for Algernon (album)</a>.</div>
